{
  "stem": "27129.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was electrician.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had my own, uh-- what do you call it?-- uh, place, you know, to work, just for electrical parts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We-- we fixed the-- the [INAUDIBLE], you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all the electrical thing and the-- the trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everything, you had to fix, because they didn't get any new stuff because of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because the war-- everybody was working for the purpose of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we had to just fix what we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that's why that was a great need for people like-- like myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I-- the-- the-- batteries, you know, I had to make from two [INAUDIBLE] to make one, or from three [INAUDIBLE] I took a part here, a part there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So to get those-- those machines, those trucks going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it was a need.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so I-- we worked until, as I said, we-- it was time to leave and go back west.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] So by that time, they boarded us on, uh-- on, uh, you know-- how did I say, those cars-- freight cars, in the same way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, we started moving back a little faster paced than when we came, because it was already more easier because the war zone was already gone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But a lot of people were going back, you know, because Russia eva-- evacuated a lot of people, especially women and children, from the war zones.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So these places got crowded more and more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So a lot of people started going back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So when we came back to Poland, we came to the border, to the Polish border, so the [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Poles ?] said, 'look, John, there's still so many Jews left.' Oh, that hit me so hard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I could cry.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
